description:
Ted Greene conducting a seminar at Boulevard Music. This is the first part of a lengthy (1.5 hours worth of footage) multi-segment master class.

*My Life with The Chord Chemist: A Memoir of Ted Greene, Apotheosis of Solo Guitar by Barbara Franklin - Available at amazon.com
http://www.amazon.com/My-Life-Chord-Chemist-Apotheosis/dp/1449575579

*Visit http://www.tedgreene.com for all things Ted
title: Ted Greene Boulevard Music Seminar 8-22-04 pt.1
fulltitle: Ted Greene Boulevard Music Seminar 8-22-04 pt.1
